{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM06_030.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x18,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "The \"Scar of the Land\"... A deep chasm, cut straight into the earth..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, it's a really amazing place... So what did you want to talk to me about...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Sophie, I'd like to ask you something. What kind of power do you believe alchemy to be?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy? Hm, well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I think it's like a power from a dream... Maybe?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I was able to meet you thanks to alchemy, and I'm able to go places with you thanks to it too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "We couldn't have come here like this if it wasn't for alchemy. Don't you think it's the stuff of dreams?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "...Yes, as you said, I believe alchemy is a wonderful power, with near limitless potential."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "However, at the same time, alchemy has another, much different side to it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Sophie. Do you have any idea how the \"Scar of the Land\" was created?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "No, not at all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "To tell the truth, the \"Scar of the Land\" was cut into the earth by alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "What!? A huge chasm like this...!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "The possibilities of alchemy are countless. Enough to make it seem like something from dreams."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "However, it also has the power to cause great calamities."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Misuse of alchemy can turn that grand, dream-like power into nightmares. Nightmares which can then turn on us."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "The form alchemy takes depends on the thoughts and desires of the alchemist using it. I want you to remember this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I get what you're saying, Plachta. But it's okay. I would never use alchemy for bad things."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Sophie..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy is such an amazing power."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I think it would be much better to use that power to help people, not do bad things with it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "...Hehe, I see. It seems I didn't need to talk to you about this, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "That's right. Did you really think I'd do bad things with alchemy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "...Hehe, you're right. I was mistaken. Anyway, we should return to the atelier."
        }
    ]
}